               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer of the Covenant, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡; Mystagogia, ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡; Absolution of the Son, ፍትሐት፡ ዘወልድ፡; For the sake of peaceful holy things, በእንተ፡ ቅድሳት፡ ሰላማዊት፡; Anaphora of Our Lord, ቅዳሴ፡ እግዚእ፡; God of the Luminaries, እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘብርሃናት፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="14v" facs="003">Fols 1r–14v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2260salota">Ṣalota kidān</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="14v" to="25v" facs="017">Fols 14v–25v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2444Temher">Tǝmhǝrta
                                                  ḫǝbuʾāt</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ትምሕርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡ ቅድመ፡ ዘትትነገር፡ እምጵርስፎራ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="25v" to="30r" facs="028">Fols 25v–30r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1398Fethat">Fǝtḥat
                                                  za-wald</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="30r" to="35v" facs="032">Fols 30r–35v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1190Baenta">Baʾǝnta
                                                  qǝddǝsāt</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus from="35v" to="50r" facs="038">Fols 35v–50r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1100Anapho">ʾAkkʷateta qʷǝrbān
                                                  za-ʾǝgziʾǝna ʾIyasus Krǝstos</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                     <locus from="50r" to="57r" facs="052">Fols 50r–57r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3083RepCh363">ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer
                                                  za-bǝrhānāt ʾǝgziʾabǝḥer za-śǝlṭānāt</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘብርሃናት፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘሥልጣናት፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘአርእስተ፡ መላእክት፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
